data.title: Actress Audrey Hepburn handing Julie Andrews her best actress Oscar for film "Mary Poppins," 1965
data.meta_description: TWO 'FAIR LADIES'-Audrey Hepburn, the film's "My Fair Lady," congratulates Julie Andrews, right, star of the stage version, on winning the best actress for her performance in film "Mary Poppins."
